        {
            "title": "葵涌籃球場2波友被偷手機 賊人馬鞍山落網",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/aab2231777d645312d72418778f4e8a1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041610594017152.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方於上周四（10日）接獲兩名男子報案，指他們將兩部手提電話放置於葵涌葵義路一籃球場旁的椅子上，其後發現該兩部手提電話被盜去，損失的財物價值共約1.8萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>葵涌分區特遣隊人員經深入調查後，今日（16日）凌晨在馬鞍山頌安邨拘捕一名46歲姓陳本地男子，他涉嫌「盜竊」正被扣留調查。案件交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第6隊跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197747/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2e58498a89d8d2689b29f3d535d52281/2025-04/2_40.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064201/即時-港聞-葵涌籃球場2波友被偷手機-賊人馬鞍山落網",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 11:11:41",
