            "title": "內地首季GDP增5.4%勝預期 零售總額增4.6% 惟未反映關稅影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f3b95797fb33d3a1ad6f0dae89bc8a1e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041610050421542.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>國家統計局公佈，今年首季中國GDP按年增長5.4%，勝市場預期。至於俗稱「三頭馬車」的經濟數據，當中3月社會消費品零售總額增5.9%、規模以上工業增加值7.7%，均勝市場預期。值得留意是，數據未反映美國加徵對等關稅的影響。\n\n</p>\n<p>今年首季社會消費品零售總額按年增長4.6%；城鎮固定資產投資增長4.2%；規模以上工業增加值增長6.5%。\n\n</p>\n<p>國統局又公佈，首季全國城鎮調查失業率平均值為5.3%；3月份失業率為5.2%，較上月下降0.2個百分點。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064191/即時-財經-內地首季GDP增5-4-勝預期-零售總額增4-6-惟未反映關稅影響",
